orea-china-effort-before-trump-term-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>强大的爆炸冲击了中国南方的高层住宅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fire-breaks-out-southern-china-residential-building-state-media-reports-2024-12-11/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，周三，中国南方城市深圳富裕地区的一座高层住宅发生强烈爆炸，震动波波及附近的摩天大楼。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fire-breaks-out-southern-china-residential-building-state-media-reports-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特朗普贸易风险迫在眉睫，中国当局正在考虑人民币贬值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/chinese-authorities-are-considering-weaker-yuan-trump-trade-risks-loom-sources-2024-12-11/</link><description>中国最高领导人和政策制定者正在考虑允许人民币在 2025 年贬值，因为他们准备迎接唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫后美国提高贸易关税的情况。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 07:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/chinese-authorities-are-considering-weaker-yuan-trump-trade-risks-loom-sources-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>股市为特朗普的胜利欢呼，但关税给 2025 年带来了未知数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/stocks-cheered-trumps-victory-tariffs-bring-unknowns-2025-2024-12-11/</link><description>经济学家的最坏情况预测描绘了一幅令人担忧的景象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 06:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/stocks-cheered-trumps-victory-tariffs-bring-unknowns-2025-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 加拿大部门寻求对关闭令进行司法审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-canada-unit-seeks-judicial-review-shutdown-orders-2024-12-11/</link><description>TikTok 的加拿大子公司表示，已向加拿大联邦法院提交紧急动议，寻求对该公司出于国家安全考虑而关闭其在该国业务的命令进行司法审查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:23:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-canada-unit-seeks-judicial-review-shutdown-orders-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>印度档案：中美贸易交火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-file-us-china-trade-crossfire-2024-12-11/</link><description>本文最初发表在每周二出版的《印度档案》时事通讯上。在此注册，了解印度的最新消息以及它对世界的重要性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-file-us-china-trade-crossfire-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉12月第一周在华销量达21,900辆，创第四季度最高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-sells-21900-evs-china-first-week-dec-highest-q4-2024-12-11/</link><description>特斯拉中国周三表示，12月第一周，美国汽车制造商特斯拉在中国销售了21,900辆电动汽车，创2024年第四季度最高单周销量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-sells-21900-evs-china-first-week-dec-highest-q4-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国导弹防御系统能否保护关岛免受中国威胁？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/can-us-missile-defense-system-shield-guam-chinese-threat-2024-12-11/</link><description>周二晚间，一枚 SM-3 拦截弹冲上关岛上空，加速飞向目标：一枚弹道导弹，其发动机短暂照亮了关岛的东北角。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 02:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/can-us-missile-defense-system-shield-guam-chinese-threat-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于投资者谨慎等待美国通胀数据，股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-11/</link><description>欧洲股市周三下跌，反映出亚洲股市的下跌，投资者谨慎等待美国通胀数据，预计美联储将再次降息，而美元则维持在两周高位附近。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 02:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示将采取“必要措施”捍卫台湾主权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-continued-surge-chinese-military-activity-2024-12-11/</link><description>中国周三表示，将采取“必要措施”捍卫国家主权，不会容忍“分裂主义”活动，因为台湾报道称中国战机再次在台湾周边地区增加，并呼吁北京停止挑衅。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:51:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-continued-surge-chinese-military-activity-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国宽松政策点燃需求希望，油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-edge-up-demand-hopes-chinas-looser-monetary-policy-2024-12-11/</link><description>周三，油价上涨 1%，因市场参与者预计，随着北京方面推出最新的促进经济增长的计划，最大进口国中国的需求将会增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:41:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-edge-up-demand-hopes-chinas-looser-monetary-policy-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>美元先于消费者物价指数上涨，人民币下跌，因中国考虑允许货币贬值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-holds-ground-ahead-cpi-aussie-wallows-near-4-month-low-2024-12-11/</link><description>周三，在备受期待的美国通胀数据公布之前，美元兑欧洲货币上涨，路透报道中国正在考虑允许明年人民币贬值，这导致人民币和其他亚洲货币走低。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-holds-ground-ahead-cpi-aussie-wallows-near-4-month-low-2024-12-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>